Package com.revature.service Description

Provides the service interfaces and classes which implement methods related to Revature batches, and their corresponding employees and associates.

The service package comprises four interfaces and four classes which implement each respective interface: the AssociateService interface and AssociateServiceImpl class, the BatchService interface and BatchServiceImpl class, the EmployeeService interface and EmployeeServiceImpl class, and the EmployeeBatchService interface and EmployeeBatchServiceImpl class. Each interface/class pair is also associated with the Associate, Batch, Employee, and EmployeeBatch classes from the com.revature.model package.

Since:
1.0
